title: Trailer Wiring Install: CURT 56000 on  Chevrolet Silverado 3500HD
description:
This video depicts the installation of the CURT 56000 5th Wheel/Gooseneck OEM wiring Extension on a 2013 Chevrolet Silverado 3500 HD.

Install Sheet:
https://www.curtmfg.com/masterlibrary/56000/installsheet/CME_56000_INS.PDF

Special Notes:
All Steps must be followed to ensure correct function of the T-Connector.  To verify proper installation once installed, test by connecting a test light or properly wired trailer.

Warning:
-This video is intended to be used as reference. Please refer to print instructions for complete installation information.
tags: CURT Trailer wiring, trailer lights, trailer brakes, how to install, curt 56000, Chevy Silverado, GMC Sierra
